Based off of Studio Liquids Visual Novel, and Majin Labels Anime of Kuroinu: Kedakaki Seijo wa Hakudaku ni Somaru. Kuroinu Rebellion is a Alternative Story in which you the Protagonist Chose to fight agenst Volt and the Kuroinu Demonic Army fighting along side many lovely ladies. This is a Game for those who enjoyed the Characters and Setting of the Anima and Visual Novel but wanted something more Vanilla unlike the Original
